application simpleLed

SHOW STATE MACHINE
sensor button: 9 DEBUG GRAPH

actuator led: 12 DEBUG GRAPH

-> day {
    -> standby {
        led <= LOW
        AFTER 500 AND button IS HIGH => on
    }

    on {
      led <= HIGH
      AFTER 500 => standby
    }

    off {
        led <= LOW
        AFTER 500 => end
    }

    end {
      led <= HIGH
      AFTER 500 AND button IS LOW => standby
    }
}